## Dev / LAN device builds (not for store)

```env
# Written automatically by: npm run cap:ios:sync / npm run cap:android:sync
# VITE_API_URL_NATIVE=http://192.168.x.x:3001

# Android emulator default fallback in the client:
# VITE_API_URL_NATIVE=http://10.0.2.2:3001

# Local web only:
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
```

